title: Sahibzadiye
description:
This Animation Movie is about 2 Younger sons of the 10th Guru of the sikhs GURU GOBIND SINGH JI. 

Made on tricentury martyrdom of the 2 Youger sons. Length of Movie is 49:02 minutes. The Movie have also the English sub-titles.

This is a religious  cinemascope movie.

This movie story tells how the mugal rulers ruling india does a treasury with the 
Guruji even after taking the oath and martyrdom their 2 younger sons when they 
rufused for conversion to muslim religion.
